# Infrastructure as Code (IaC) with Terraform on GCP

This project automates infrastructure provisioning on GCP using Terraform. It focuses on reusable modules, environment isolation, and best practices for cloud-native resource management.

## Features
- Provisioned Compute Engine instances and IAM roles
- Used variables, outputs, and modules for flexibility
- Managed infrastructure lifecycle with `terraform plan` and `apply`
- Version-controlled Terraform code using Git

## Tools & Technologies
- Terraform
- Google Cloud Platform
- Compute Engine
- IAM

## Skills Demonstrated
✅ Infrastructure as Code (IaC)  
✅ Terraform state and modules  
✅ Reproducible cloud environments
